Package: marinedatashiny
Title: Marine Data Statistics Graphs
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Gokhan",
           family = "KOCTURK",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "gokhankocturk7@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Application is based on Marine data provided by APPSILON. Users can select ship type and name
    from dropdown lists. 
    On "Map" tab: Users can see information about a selected ship's longest move. 
    On "Statistics" tab: Users can see summary statistics for average distance and average speed.
    On "Graphs" tab: Users can see the fastest 5 ships in selected ship type
